{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "丽雅和尤蒂尔\\n开始对“黑色魔兽”展开调查。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "根据得到的线索，\\n他们来到了某个地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "根据调查，接连有人目击到\\n变种魔兽的地方就是这一带了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里或许会有\\n与“黑色魔兽”有关的线索……\\n嗯？那是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "帝国兵！？为什么会在这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "形迹可疑，我们跟过去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这种地方居然有个洞穴……\\n啊！丽雅！快看那边！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "那是……魔法阵？\\n摆在魔法阵中央的，是魔兽的肉块吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵1",
            "context": "仪式魔法已经准备完毕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "嗯，那就开始吧。以这肉块为媒介……\\n生成新的“黑色魔兽”吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵1",
            "context": "这次终于成功了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "不，虽说看起来很像，\\n但跟原种还是差太远，啧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵1",
            "context": "那这家伙也随便扔给哪个部队吧。\\n喂，把它带走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这到底是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵2",
            "context": "啊！有入侵者！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "嗯？你们是……“叛变的王子”\\n和“憎恨魔兽的造反者”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "王子和骑士居然在这里偷看，\\n呵呵呵，真是不像话啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "你们到底在这里干什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "呵呵呵，既然都看到了，\\n再笨的脑袋也该明白了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "没错！这是终极的实验！\\n我们正在创造\\n那“黑色魔兽”的复制品！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "“黑色魔兽”的复制品？\\n这种事怎么可能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "正常来说，无论用什么样的魔法\\n都没法实现吧。但我们拥有\\n能将不可能变为可能的材料。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "那就是，这“黑色魔兽”的肉块！\\n有这个当媒介，理论上是可行的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "居然是那头魔兽的肉块！？\\n你们是怎么弄到这种东西的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "这可多亏了你父亲啊，\\n“憎恨魔兽的造反者”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "诶？多亏了父亲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "10年前，那魔兽\\n在与你父亲的战斗中受了伤。\\n战场上留下了魔兽被砍下的肉块。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "然而那肉块却有着令人惊异的再生能力。\\n王国害怕肉块被人滥用\\n而悄悄将其封印。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此！你们解开了封印，\\n在这里进行仪式魔法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "没错。不过现在只能弄出一些\\n粗制滥造的复制品而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而那些复制品正是最近传言的元凶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "“黑色魔兽”被称作最凶恶的魔兽。\\n能弄伤它的，也许过去和将来\\n也都只有那位骑士了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "所以，我们之所以能用这肉块\\n来进行实验，可都是多亏了你父亲啊，\\n“憎恨魔兽的造反者”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "怎、怎么会……这种事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "而且，至今为止我们生成的\\n复制品都已配备给我军。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "虽说是劣质品，但也远强于普通的魔兽。\\n如今应该已经作为帝国的战力\\n在各地大肆进行破坏了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "而这一切，我们帝国都得向\\n你父亲表示衷心的感谢啊！\\n啊哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "父亲他……父亲他才不是\\n为了这种事而拼死战斗的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "才不是为了你们这些家伙\\n丢掉性命的啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "丽雅！冷静点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵2",
            "context": "这家伙，打算跟这么多人交战吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "哼，无畏的挣扎而已。\\n赶紧把她收拾掉！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "冷静点，丽雅！敌我战力悬殊，\\n不要着急，我们好好配合……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "父亲他……父亲他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "危险！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "呃！？尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我没事，我们赶紧合力\\n把这些家伙打倒吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "嗯、嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国魔法师",
            "context": "哇啊……饶、饶命！\\n我什么都愿意做，所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "乖乖把那魔兽的肉块交给我们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "抱歉，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "居然被愤怒冲昏了头脑……\\n我真是愧为骑士。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "要是我站在你的立场上……\\n也没有自信能够冷静下来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "总之我们先把这肉块带回去吧。\\n耶梦加得也许知道该如何封印这东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "之后，尤蒂尔等人\\n借助碧龙的智慧\\n成功封印了魔兽的肉块。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "丽雅，睡不着吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "尤蒂尔……\\n我又想起了过去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "那天早上……\\n父亲还陪我练剑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "然后说下次还会再陪我练剑，\\n就去执行任务了，\\n却再也没能回来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "我偶尔会这样想……\\n要是父亲没有遇到“黑色魔兽”，\\n也许现在还在我身边吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "即便如此……父亲是为保护人们而战死。\\n我作为骑士之女\\n接受了这一事实，生活至今。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "然而，父亲所做的一切，\\n如今却成了战祸的根源。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "这样的话，\\n父亲拼命战斗的意义何在！？\\n父亲到底是为了什么才丧命的！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "为什么父亲……\\n父亲他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "丽雅……\\n你的父亲做了骑士应该做的事。\\n他做的事并非毫无意义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "是……这样吗……\\n不过，我也想相信……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "那场战斗留给我们的，\\n一定不止这些。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "况且帝国军手上还有\\n“黑色魔兽”的复制品，\\n没时间让我们长吁短叹了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，谢谢你。\\n明天起我会继续努力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_02_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
